        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are browned, transfer them to a clean plate and set aside (these will finish cooking in the sauce later!)</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>and <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
