    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once tender, add 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and the<strong> remaining garlic </strong>to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[255ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>remaining dried thyme</strong> and your<strong> soft cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
